parameters: Yawn~~~
Lately, the dormitory has been noisy...
Hm? You seem to be breathing heavily... Is something wrong?
If I could use magic... I'm sure I could do anything.
I think I can erase even unpleasant memories.
Hey, I'm sleepy... zzz.
This...this is the men's restroom...
I, too, someday... Ah, like Anastasia-sama...
I... I will become a court sorceress.
This is the Magic Academy.
This...is not a place for indecent things...
Anastasia-sama... W-We... admire... you...
Genius is always accompanied by rumors...

But those rumors are just too vulgar... Please don't disappoint me too
much.

The exams here are not only difficult in practical skills, but also in
paper tests...
To become a sorcerer, you need to be able to study...
Studying... physical education... in moderation... right.
Even if you're skilled in powerful sorcery and have a sharp mind...
What's important is... your humanity.

Impure heterosexual relationships may result in expulsion... that's
also a possibility, you know...

Lately... I've been hearing rumors that don't seem appropriate for
this academy...

I can't believe a child like you... something like that... n-no...
it's nothing...

There's a student who can't be reached. Maybe they ran away because
our school is strict?
Even the students we couldn't contact have returned...
So, we're going back to our normal school life again.
...Sigh.
Rumors don't spread where there's no fire...
So that means it's true...
I do remember it clearly.
You were being done something by a witch!!
...Right?

[Commoner Student] Someday, I will become a strong person who can't be
defeated by anyone, just like Lady Anastasia.
